github.setup            deweller switchaudio-osx 1.0.0
license                 MIT
categories              audio
platforms               darwin
maintainers             gmail.com:israelchauca

description             A command-line utility to switch the audio source on Mac OS X.
long_description        This utility switches the audio source for Mac OS X. \
                        You specify the name of the audio source, such as \
                        Built-in Digital Output, and the utility switches the \
                        source immediately without any GUI interaction.

